  and comprehensive view on international relations, and prepare them for an international career. As the main program language is English,
  the graduates having a diploma on international relations or political science from a university in or outside Kyrgyzstan must be qualified
  in English in order to be accepted for this program. If they fail in English proficiency examination of our university, they have to attend
  preparatory school of our university for one year. If the number of applicants, who are qualified in English, is less than 8, the program will
